e\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2016-06-21</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Artsetsocietes.org&amp;rft.atitle=Arts+%26+Soci%C3%A9t%C3%A9s&amp;rft.date=2006-06-29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.artsetsocietes.org%2Fa%2Fa-berggruen.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOlivier+Berggruen\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20160804201828/http://www.metmuseum.org/~/media/Files/About/Annual%20Reports/2014-2015/Annual%20Report%202015%20Visiting%20Committees.pdf\">[1]</a> </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sismus.org/museums/budget/Guggenheim/GMB.pdf\">\"Guggenheim Museum Bilbao\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <i>Sismus.org</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2016-06-21</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Sismus.org&amp;rft.atitle=Guggenheim+Museum+Bilbao&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sismus.org%2Fmuseums%2Fbudget%2FGuggenheim%2FGMB.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOlivier+Berggruen\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-huff-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-huff_8-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-huff_8-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web